law.history: Repealed 1964 Ky. Acts ch. 157, sec. 18. -- Amended 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 227, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 3766d-3a, 3766d-3c, 3766d-7.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Department may acquire, improve and operate parks; fees and charges.
